text: Achim Stadler (born 27 August 1961) is a German former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:People from Speyer Category:German male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of West Germany Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rhineland-Palatinate
